file.name: RequestBodyService.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: User service
  description: User service
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /create:
    post:
      summary: Creates a new user.
      operationId: create
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
      responses:
        201:
          description: User created
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        status:
          type: integer
          description: User Status
          format: int32
          enum:
            - 1
            - 2
            - 3
      example:
        id: 123
        firstName: Ivan
        secondName: Petrov
        status: 1
